国家的画廊及美术馆展出。其出版物 Smells Like Content (Endless Editions)被收录于纽约MoMa图书馆艺术家藏书(artists’ book collection of the MoMA Library, New York)。</span></section><section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: left;text-decoration: underline;\">https://cole-lu.com/</span></section><section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: left;text-decoration: underline;\">@colelu</span></section><section><br  /></section><section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"810\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"627\" data-ratio=\"1.4831683168316832\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/pLhvdZgejGQmYHW1jLw1Yg45ePQSoqMnpsSlSdZ1ySIrt5TYQhSedlHGDibHvegj5FdnsCknq6blLARUXQuubVA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"505\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\"  /></section><section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">娜布其&nbsp;Nabuqi</span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(119, 119, 119);color: rgb(119, 119, 119);font-family: Arial;font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: left;\">198